front.title: •Hiding In The Garbage
front.gametext: Use 2 Force to deploy on your side of table. At any time, you may declare a card type. Use Force one by one, revealing each card used, until a card of that type is revealed (take it into hand) or Force Pile is depleted.
front.lore: Rebels often exploit loopholes in Imperial procedures to gain an advantage.

pulledBy: We Wish To Board At Once
